<view class="page search-page">
  <view class="search-head">
    <view class="search-kicker">
      <text class="eyebrow">找东西</text>
    </view>
    <text class="page-title search-title">想找什么？</text>
  </view>

  <view class="search-box">
    <view class="search-mark"></view>
    <input
      class="search-input"
      placeholder="输入物品名称、颜色或特征"
      value="{{query}}"
      confirm-type="search"
      bindinput="inputQuery"
      bindconfirm="submitSearch"
    />
  </view>

  <view class="chips">
    <view
      wx:for="{{examples}}"
      wx:key="*this"
      class="chip"
      data-query="{{item}}"
      bindtap="useExample"
    >{{item}}</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-row">
    <text class="section-heading">{{resultHeading}}</text>
    <text class="text-link">按相关度</text>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{hasResults}}" class="result-stack">
    <search-result-card
      wx:for="{{results}}"
      wx:key="resultId"
      result="{{item}}"
      bind:open="openResult"
    ></search-result-card>
  </view>
  <view wx:if="{{showEmptyResults}}" class="empty-state with-xiaolan">
    <view class="xiaolan-row">
      <image class="xiaolan-avatar" mode="aspectFit" src="/assets/xiaolan-sloth.svg"></image>
      <view class="xiaolan-copy">
        <text class="xiaolan-name">小懒没有找到匹配物品</text>
        <text>换一个更宽泛的词试试，比如“书”或“蓝色”。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view wx:if="{{showSearchHint}}" class="empty-state with-xiaolan">
    <view class="xiaolan-row">
      <image class="xiaolan-avatar" mode="aspectFit" src="/assets/xiaolan-sloth.svg"></image>
      <view class="xiaolan-copy">
        <text class="xiaolan-name">小懒会一起看名称和特征</text>
        <text>保存容器后，搜索会覆盖名称、别名、颜色、可见文字和关键特征。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <button class="empty-action" bindtap="goCapture">先拍一箱</button>
  </view>

  <view class="bottom-nav">
    <view class="nav-item" bindtap="goHome">
      <view class="nav-icon"></view>
      <text>首页</text>
    </view>
    <view class="nav-item active">
      <view class="nav-icon search"></view>
      <text>找东西</text>
    </view>
    <view class="nav-item" bindtap="showContainers">
      <view class="nav-icon box"></view>
      <text>容器</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
